# Hero Video Placeholder

To add a hero background video:

1. Replace this file with your actual MP4 video
2. Recommended specs:
   - Duration: 10-30 seconds
   - Resolution: 1920x1080 or higher
   - Format: MP4 (H.264 codec)
   - File size: Under 5MB for optimal loading
   - Loop: Yes (seamless loop recommended)

3. Ensure the video is optimized for web:
   - Use appropriate compression
   - Consider creating multiple formats (WebM, MP4) for browser compatibility
   - Add a poster image as fallback